    <h2 class="text-3xl font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-6">What is AI automation for event management?</h2>
    <p class="text-white mb-4">
      AI automation for event management is the application of artificial intelligence to streamline, optimize, and enhance every stage of the event lifecycle. Unlike general business automation, it uses intelligent algorithms specifically designed to handle the dynamic and complex variables of event coordination, from initial registration to post-event analytics. This technology marks a significant evolution from manual spreadsheets and disconnected tools to integrated, intelligent workflows that anticipate needs and automate responses.
    </p>
    <p class="text-white mb-6">
